# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# PRODUCTION (set in Vercel — do not commit real keys)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Frontend project (Vercel):
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_BACKEND_URL=https://your-backend.vercel.app   (or Railway URL)
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=...
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=...
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=...
#
# Backend project (Vercel or other host):
#   SUPABASE_URL=...
#   SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=...
#   SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=...
#   FRONTEND_URL=https://your-frontend.vercel.app
#   PORT=3001   (or host-provided)
#   GEMINI_API_KEY=...
#
# After changing NEXT_PUBLIC_* on Vercel → Redeploy (values are baked at build).
